questionsAndAnswers.question: Requirements to Get Started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: (1) Domain & Hosting with Cpanel (2) Your WordPress Admin credentials  (3) Logo   (4) Content for WordPress website  pages like (Home, About, Services)  (5)  Brief requirements for a website like what type of website we need to build, the reference design or website

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is Domain & Hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: The domain is the address of your website that people type in the browserâ€™s URL bar to visit your website and Web hosting is the place where all the files of your website exist.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you Provide Hosting & Domain?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, we do not provide it, you need to purchase a domain and hosting like from these best providers (Blue host, Hostinger, and Host Gator

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer Services WordPress Ecommerce store
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we can create an eCommerce WordPress store using WordPress Woccomerce and integrate different payment gateways

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide WordPress website Speed Optimizations too?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we provide! We can make your website faster to load in under 3 sec because customers like the website which is fast and Google too ) :

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide SEO Services too ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes! We provide! We provide On-page SEO and Off-Page SEO too! Reach us for consulting more in-depth

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you do NFT Landing Pages Design ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes! We do! We design NFT Landing Pages using WordPress as well as using custom HTML, CSS, and Bootstrap!

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I change/edit the content later on the website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
Even if you don't know any programming language, you can change/edit or modify the content on the website very easily.
We provide Video Guidance after completion that how can you manage and edit the content of the website by yourself (if you want)

questionsAndAnswers.question: Are you available for custom orders?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I am available for a custom order

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you Provide Support After completion?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes we do provide 15 days of free support and after that, we offer different Maintenance services, you can check that gig
